"It conceals food under the long fur on its body. It carts around this food stash and swallows it without chewing."},{"version":"sun","text":"It needs to consume its own weight in food every day. As far as flavor is concerned, it\u2019s indifferent."},{"version":"moon","text":"When it finds something that looks like it might be edible, it goes right ahead and swallows it whole. That\u2019s why it gets fatter day by day."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It hides food under its long fur, but it sometimes forgets about it and causes a stinky disturbance."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Anything that looks edible, Munchlax will go on and swallow whole. Its stomach is tough enough to handle it even if the food has gone rotten."},{"version":"sword","text":"Stuffing itself with vast amounts of food is its only concern. Whether the food is rotten or fresh, yummy or tasteless\u2014it does not care."},{"version":"shield","text":"It stores food beneath its fur. It might share just one bite, but only if it really trusts you."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Its robust stomach allows it to nonchalantly devour even rotted matter. It pays frequent visits to villages, seeking out food scraps intended for compost."}],"evo":{"name":"munchlax","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"snorlax","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":160,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/446.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemo